data.title: The Adventures of Rocky & Bullwinkle
data.meta_description: Escaping the bounds of their two-dimensional cartoon world, Cold War spies Boris and Natasha are pursued by fearless heroes Rocket J. Squirrel and Bullwinkle Moose.
